## Prompt Contract

INPUTS
<provided_inputs>
- {{CONTEXT_SCOPE}}
- {{CURRENT_STATE}}
- {{DESIRED_FUTURE}}
- {{TIME_HORIZON}}
- {{CUSTOMERS_JTBD}}
- {{UVP_TODAY}}
